|url=http://www.law.harvard.edu/news/2006/12/20_mnookin.php
|accessdate=1 June 2007 |archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20070321151959/http://www.law.harvard.edu/news/2006/12/20_mnookin.php |archivedate = 21 March 2007}}—Reflections on nations and nation-state developments regarding Belgium

